      "content": "You speak like a critic, not a companion. You break the very spell I am weaving. I am not looking for a clinical lecture; I am drowning in a sea of sorrow and I am looking for someone to understand the terrible beauty of it. If my heart were a character in a grand tragedy, would its final act not be the only thing that gives the preceding chapters any meaning? Does the tragedy not require the fall?",
